data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Lawrence Township! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem is a perfect blend of comfort and style. Step into the heart of the home-a bright and inviting eat-in kitchen, ideal for family gatherings and casual meals. Take note of the modern light fixtures in the lower level! The formal dining room adds a touch of elegance, perfect for hosting dinner parties.  With both a living and family room, there's plenty of space for relaxation and entertainment. Imagine cozy evenings by the fireplace or movie nights with loved ones. The new flooring throughout adds a modern touch, providing a seamless flow from room to room.  Retreat to the primary bathroom, featuring a large tub for a luxurious soak after a long day. The entire home is painted in neutral colors, creating a serene atmosphere and allowing your personal style to shine.  Convenience is key with this Lawrence Township location. Proximity to shopping and dining means you're never far from the best amenities. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home!  Citizens Energy Group averages $50.00 per month and AES averages $100.00 per month.
